## 13. Validation Commands By Zone

Frontend:

```bash
pnpm --filter @zoc-studio/frontend typecheck
pnpm --filter @zoc-studio/frontend test
pnpm --filter @zoc-studio/frontend lint
```

Python agent:

```bash
pytest services/agent/tests
```

Rust:

```bash
cargo check --workspace
cargo test --workspace
```

Shared schema:

```bash
pnpm schema:generate
pnpm --filter @zoc-studio/shared-types typecheck
```

Whole repo:

```bash
make check
pnpm check
```

Documentation-only changes:

```bash
test -f doc/hybrid.me
```

